        },
        {
          "character": "鬼判",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。姻缘簿呈上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来有这桩公案。藏过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鬼判",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兴娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那崔兴哥名唤崔嗣宗，与你有一载魂魄夫妻之分。一年后，就是你妹子庆娘与\n他续上此姻也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然被我猜着了。妹子吓，你的命倒强似我的。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兴娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炳灵公 （醉春风） 恁休羡，伊家小妹，与他做夫妻。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却不道，他俩个福俱齐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "又不曾同醪合卺、何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贱妾可得见崔嗣宗一面？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炳灵公 （醉春风） 吃个筵席。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷吓，贱妾空有夫妻名分，若得一见，不枉我一生一死㖸。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炳灵公 （醉春风） 怎生叫划地里相傍相依。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（醉春风） 俺如今许你把幽情遂。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只教恁游魂去一载才回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贱妾与崔嗣宗有何为证？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炳灵公 （醉春风） 这情关须不是俺冥司职，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问你那原聘物，有甚么东西。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "由原聘金凤钗在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "金凤钗。藏过了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炳灵公 （斗鹌鹑） 俺也只是闲口评论，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "问因甚来回得这首尾。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贱妾出世可得罪么？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炳灵公 （斗鹌鹑） 只限恁今日今年，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刚道那明春明岁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贱妾怎敢违限。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炳灵公 （斗鹌鹑） 谁怕恁将咱定限违，"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兴娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（斗鹌鹑） 咱只是怜恤伊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不能够的了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（斗鹌鹑） 你魂已入枉死城中哩，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "休指望回生案底。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "鬼判。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鬼判",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "换扬州当境土司过来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鬼判",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "土司走动。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "爷爷，贱妾可能再得轮回人世么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兴娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炳灵公 （上小楼） 只要恁依咱教诲，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "身上仙梯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "伊家小妹同纡霞帔。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贱妾是死的，妹是活的，怎生相比。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "说哪里话来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（上小楼） 死和生那些儿兴废。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若得如此，我好喜也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "鬼判",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这里来。扬州土司唤到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "土司",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扬州土司见大帝，有何法旨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你就是何兴娘家当境土司么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "土司",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那何兴娘与崔嗣宗有一年魂魄夫妻之分，一载后到本司这里交割，不得有违。"
        },
        {
          "character": "土司",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领法旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "炳灵公",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兴娘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "何兴娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "炳灵公 （煞尾） 愁只愁，夫妻未会，生拆离。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喜只喜，同胞小妹，为继室。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想人间妒妇，那管亲同契。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不妒如伊，更谁比。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
